_sText:
Beta 6 (I had some testing/balancing in between 3 and 6)

Changelog:
-Lip added to sauna doors.
-Flying model brought down to earth.
-Fence glitch fixed.
-CTs can no longer press the buttons through the fence.
-Added another secret grenade.
-Added 8 units to longjump.
-The Shark button now works.
-All buttons now have Keycard Sound rather than techblip.
-Added some prop_statics.
-Shark now swims forwards.
-Tweaked the fire extinguisher damage.

Again, please report any bugs.

Enjoy

ps. There are 64 spawn points.
